## Build Instructions

Maven and Java 17 are required (not yet installed on this system). See [README.md](file:///c:/Users/Shahid/Documents/projects%20and%20experiments/experiments/plugins/rpg%20spellcaster/README.md) for full setup instructions, or run [build.bat](file:///c:/Users/Shahid/Documents/projects%20and%20experiments/experiments/plugins/rpg%20spellcaster/build.bat) which auto-detects and guides you.

```powershell
# After installing Java 17 + Maven:
cd "rpg spellcaster"
mvn clean package
# → target/rpg-spellcaster-1.0.0.jar
```

---

## In-Game Quick Start

```
/wand gravity_pull            → right-click → spiral vortex pulls enemies
/wand homing_missile 2        → right-click → tracking fireball
/wand wall_of_fire 3          → right-click → fire wall perpendicular to gaze
/wand nova_blast              → right-click → radial shockwave burst
/spellcaster list             → show all spells
```
